&lt;li&gt;Over-time and weekend availability, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PERFORMANCE REVIEW AND CHECK-INS SCHEDULE&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weekly team huddles and bi-annual 1:1s.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Annual performance review.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary from $22/hour&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time position with competitive compensation and benefits. We are an Equal Opportunity Employer. Position is based at APPARATUS PRODUCTION in Red Hook. Must be legally authorized to work in the U.S. without sponsorship.&lt;/p&gt;

